{"id": "32545", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=32545", "title": "War Hammers", "text": "War Hammers are a &lt;a href=\"Weapon%20Class\"&gt;class&lt;/a&gt; of one-handed melee weapon that shares the Hammers &lt;a href=\"Weapon%20Proficiency\"&gt;weapon proficiency&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Throwing%20Hammers\"&gt;Throwing Hammers&lt;/a&gt; in all games except for classic Baldur's Gate, in which they shared the Blunt Weapons category with &lt;a href=\"Clubs\"&gt;Clubs&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Maces\"&gt;Maces&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Quarterstaves\"&gt;Quarterstaves&lt;/a&gt;. They cannot be used by the following &lt;a href=\"Classes\"&gt;character classes&lt;/a&gt; and class kits: Beast Master, Druid (including Fighter/Druid) Monk, Shaman, Mage, Sorcerer and Thief. The basic War Hammer has a range of 1ft, deals 1d4+1 crushing damage with a speed factor of 5 and requires a Strength of 9 to use.\nList of War Hammers.\n&lt;tabber&gt;\nIn Baldur's Gate = &lt;dpl&gt;\nnamespace = \ncategory = Hammers\ncategory = Items in Baldur's Gate|Items, added by Tales of the Sword Coast|Items in Tales of the Sword Coast|Items, new in Tales of the Sword Coast|Items in Baldur's Gate (Enhanced Edition)|Items, new in Baldur's Gate (Enhanced Edition)\nnotcategory = Cut items\nnotcategory = Mod items\nordermethod = sortkey\nuses = Template:Infobox item\ninclude = {Infobox item}.list weapons|hide_type=yes|dpl_game=bg1\nformat = ,\\n,\n&lt;/dpl&gt;\nIn Siege of Dragonspear = &lt;dpl&gt;\nnamespace = \ncategory = Hammers\ncategory = Items, added by Siege of Dragonspear|Items in Siege of Dragonspear|Items, new in Siege of Dragonspear\nnotcategory = Cut items\nnotcategory = Mod items\nordermethod = sortkey\nuses = Template:Infobox item\ninclude = {Infobox item}.list weapons|hide_type=yes|dpl_game=sod\nformat = ,\\n,\n&lt;/dpl&gt;\nIn Shadows of Amn = &lt;dpl&gt;\nnamespace = \ncategory = Hammers\ncategory = Items in Shadows of Amn|Items in Shadows of 