{"id": "35802", "revid": "31997783", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=35802", "title": "Where's Wilson?", "text": "The bear companion, &lt;a href=\"Wilson\"&gt;Wilson&lt;/a&gt;, can be found in the &lt;a href=\"Heretic%20Temple\"&gt;Heretic Temple&lt;/a&gt; (an area unlocked during &lt;a href=\"Rasaad%27s%20Journey\"&gt;Rasaad's Journey&lt;/a&gt;). He is held prisoner by &lt;a href=\"Jolstead\"&gt;Jolstead&lt;/a&gt; and can be freed (see &lt;a href=\"Heretic%20Temple\"&gt;Heretic Temple&lt;/a&gt;). \nHe will vanish if the &lt;a href=\"Rasaad%27s%20Journey\"&gt;Rasaad's Journey&lt;/a&gt; quest is brought to an end, so it is recommended to recruit the bear and bring him to &lt;a href=\"Zaviak\"&gt;Zaviak&lt;/a&gt; as soon as possible once you unlock the &lt;a href=\"Heretic%20Temple\"&gt;Heretic Temple&lt;/a&gt; area. \nOnce freed, &lt;a href=\"Wilson\"&gt;Wilson&lt;/a&gt; will flee and wait at\u00a0the northwestern edge of the map, close to where you first enter. Recruit &lt;a href=\"Wilson\"&gt;Wilson&lt;/a&gt;, bring him to &lt;a href=\"Zaviak\"&gt;Zaviak&lt;/a&gt; and get the &lt;a href=\"Green%20Dragon%20Potion\"&gt;Green Dragon Potion&lt;/a&gt; (5x) reward.\nLike the other quests taking place within the Neera's Hidden Refuge quest, it's recommended that this quest is completed before &lt;a href=\"Neera%27s%20Hidden%20Refuge%23Finding%20Daxus\"&gt;Finding Daxus&lt;/a&gt;.\nNotes.\nIt is completely possible to negotiate the release of &lt;a href=\"Wilson\"&gt;Wilson&lt;/a&gt; and still miss the opportunity to recruit him as a companion. \nYou MUST speak with Wilson prior to conversing with &lt;a href=\"Jolstead\"&gt;Jolstead&lt;/a&gt;, otherwise you will simply receive 5000 experience points for his release, but not be able to complete the quest."}
