{"id": "5043", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5043", "title": "Call Lightning", "text": "Call Lightning is a 3rd level &lt;a href=\"priest%20spell\"&gt;priest spell&lt;/a&gt; only usable by &lt;a href=\"druid\"&gt;druid&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"shaman\"&gt;shaman&lt;/a&gt;s, and &lt;a href=\"ranger\"&gt;ranger&lt;/a&gt;s. It allows the caster to call bolts of lightning upon enemies.\nMod content.\n&lt;a href=\"Spell%20Revisions\"&gt;Spell Revisions&lt;/a&gt; mod has changed this divine spell, revising its effects, duration, saving throw and description. See below:\nCall Lightning\nLevel: 3\nSchool: Alteration\nSphere: Weather\nRange: Long\nDuration: Special\nCasting Time: 1 round\nArea of Effect: 360\u2019 radius\nSaving Throw: Breath half\nImmediately upon completion of the spell, and once per round thereafter, the caster causes a 30-foot-long vertical bolt of lightning to come crashing down upon an enemy. The spell has a duration of one round for every three levels of the caster, up to a maximum of 5 rounds at 15th level. The lightning will strike first at the target of the spell, dealing 6d6 points of electrical damage, with a successful save vs. breath at -2 reducing this to half. For the remainder of the storm\u2019s duration, the bolts will strike out randomly at the enemies of the caster.\nThis spell is only usable by Druid/Ranger/Shaman classes."}
{"id": "13203", "revid": "53053884", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=13203", "title": "Call Woodland Beings", "text": "Call Woodland Beings is a 4th level &lt;a href=\"priest%20spell\"&gt;priest spell&lt;/a&gt; only usable by &lt;a href=\"druid\"&gt;druid&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"shaman\"&gt;shaman&lt;/a&gt;s. It will summon forth a spellcasting nymph to aid the spell caster.\nGameplay.\nThe summoned nymph will utilize the following spells which are cast as a level 5 priest:\nIf the nymph has not been ordered to do anything and there's not an enemy in sight to attack, she will usually cast a Barkskin on herself, which doesn't expend the one cast of this spell she has available.\nThe nymph has\u00a0very low &lt;a href=\"HP\"&gt;HP&lt;/a&gt; and a poor &lt;a href=\"Armor%20Class\"&gt;Armor Class&lt;/a&gt;, making its main advantage its spell slot value (i.e., A well-utilized nymph can turn a single 4th level spell slot into multiple higher level priest spells).\nDespite being considered a level 5 caster, some of the nymph's spells are stronger than they appear because they're coded with minimums based on when a priest (druid, cleric, etc.) can access them. For example, the description of the priest \"Confusion\" spell states that it lasts for 1 round/2 levels, so a caster of level 5 should (in theory) only get 2 rounds, but it actually lasts for 7 rounds (as it's normally only available to a divine caster of level 14 and upwards).\nThe nymph's combat statistics, which differ from its &lt;a href=\"Nymph\"&gt;normal creature version&lt;/a&gt;, are shown below.\nMod content.\nInstallation of the &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Revisions\"&gt;Spell Revisions&lt;/a&gt; Mod provides a new version of this spell as follows:\nCall Woodland Beings \nLevel: 4 \nSchool: Conjuration \nSphere: Animal \nRange: Medium \nDuration: 3 turns \nCasting Time: 1 round \nArea of Effect: Special \nSaving Throw: None \n1-7th: 1 hamadryad \n9th: 2 hamadryads \n11th: 2 hamadryads, 1 nymph \nThe summoned beings will aid the caster by whatever means they possess, staying until the spell duration expires.\nHamadryad (4 Hit Dice): \nSTR 10, DEX 18, CON 12, INT 14, WIS 14, CHA 18; AL Neutral \nHP 32, AC 3, THAC0 14, Saving Throws 12/16/12/14/16 \n2 Attacks Per Round, 1d6+1 missile (Short Bow &amp; arrows +1) \nSpecial Qualities: \nMagic Resistance 75% \nMemorized Spells: \n1st Level: Cure Light Wounds (x2), Entangle (x2), Shillelagh, Doom \n2nd Level: Barkskin, Charm Person or Animal (x2), Resist Elements, Slow Poison \nNymph (7 Hit Dice): \nSTR 10, DEX 17, CON 12, INT 16, WIS 17, CHA 19; AL Neutral Good \nHP 42, AC 3, THAC0 15, Saving Throws 12/10/12/14/10 \n1 Attack Per Round, 1d4 Crushing (Touch +0) \nSpecial Qualities: \nMagic Resistance 50% \nMemorized Spells: \n1st Level: Cure Light Wounds (x2), Entangle (x2), Shillelagh, Doom \n2nd Level: Barkskin, Charm Person or Animal (x2), Resist Elements, Slow Poison \n3rd Level: Call Lightning, Hold Person or Animal, Summon Insects \n4the Level: Animal Summoning IV"}
