{"id": "25619", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=25619", "title": "Candlekeep Caves", "text": "The Candlekeep Caves is the final dungeon encountered beneath the &lt;a href=\"Candlekeep%20Library\"&gt;Candlekeep Library&lt;/a&gt;. The caves are accessed from the &lt;a href=\"Candlekeep%20Catacombs%20Level%202\"&gt;second level&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"Candlekeep%20Catacombs\"&gt;catacombs&lt;/a&gt;. The entrance is at the northern end of the caves, and the southern exit returns the party to the outside world, whereupon the party finds themselves next to the outer wall of the &lt;a href=\"Candlekeep\"&gt;Keep&lt;/a&gt;."}
