{"id": "4773", "revid": "49135869", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4773", "title": "Implosion", "text": "Implosion is a &lt;a href=\"High-level%20class%20ability\"&gt;High-level class ability&lt;/a&gt; usable by &lt;a href=\"Cleric\"&gt;Cleric&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Druid\"&gt;Druid&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Shaman\"&gt;Shaman&lt;/a&gt; divine casters.\nGameplay.\nAll spell effects ignore &lt;a href=\"Magic%20resistance\"&gt;Magic resistance&lt;/a&gt;.\nBecause the spell has no school, &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Immunity\"&gt;Spell Immunity&lt;/a&gt; is not effective and &lt;a href=\"Specialist%20Mage\"&gt;Specialist Mage&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"Cleric\"&gt;Cleric&lt;/a&gt; dual classes will not enjoy saving throw modifications.\nThe only enemies who will cast this spell against the party are &lt;a href=\"Sendai\"&gt;Sendai&lt;/a&gt; (the original, not her clones) and &lt;a href=\"Demogorgon\"&gt;Demogorgon&lt;/a&gt;.\nThis spell can be particularly deadly due to its magic resistance-bypassing, no saving throw, and 1 round &lt;a href=\"Held\"&gt;Hold Creature&lt;/a&gt; effect using &lt;a href=\"Opcode\"&gt;Opcode&lt;/a&gt; 175 (which is not addressed in the spell description). \nThe spell's internal effects are &lt;a href=\"Power%20level\"&gt;Power level&lt;/a&gt; 7. As such, they can be mitigated via any kind single-target spell protection that has a capacity to protect against that power level, for example &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Deflection\"&gt;Spell Deflection&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Shield%20of%20the%20Archons\"&gt;Shield of the Archons&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Turning\"&gt;Spell Turning&lt;/a&gt;.\nA &lt;a href=\"Stoneskin\"&gt;Stoneskin&lt;/a&gt; (1-skin) is enough to defend against the crushing damage.\nMod Content.\n&lt;a href=\"Spell%20Revisions\"&gt;Spell Revisions&lt;/a&gt; mod has changed this Divine HLA spell, revising its school, effects, casting time, saving throw and description:\nImplosion\nLevel: Quest\nSchool: Alteration\nSphere: Combat, Numbers\nRange: Long\nDuration: 1 round\nCasting Time: 7\nArea of Effect: 1 creature\nSaving Throw: Death partial\nThis fearsome spell creates a destructive resonance in a corporeal creature\u2019s body, causing it to collapse in on itself, crushing it to death. The spell does 20d8 points of crushing damage, and holds the target for 1 round. The victim can save vs. death at a -6 penalty to halve the damage.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Sword%20Coast%20Stratagems\"&gt;Sword Coast Stratagems&lt;/a&gt; mod's AI will typically recognize if a targeted creature is immune to crushing damage or has an active Stoneskin protection. If so, the caster may use a different attack/spell instead, or choose another target."}
